1Data were collected from 2017-11-03 to 2018-12-09. Participants unable to meet the eyetracking device requirements (e.g. Chrome and Firefox, webcam, laptop or desktop) were placed in the behavioral version of dotprobe. Reasons include: participant dropout, no webcam present on the device (n=20, 10%) and blocked access of the webcam by the participants browser (n=19, 9%).
Once completing the Pre-Questionnaire on REDCap, participants are redirected to the task. Possible reasons for the drop off between Pre-Questionnaire (n=285) and Task (n=208) samples can be due to: Technical error during redirect, and disinterest in continuing to participate in the experiment.
